{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/spooktacularkit\/provisioning"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/Provisioning","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"article","topicSections":[{"anchor":"Provisioning-Modes","title":"Provisioning Modes","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/diskInject","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/ssh","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/agent","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/sharedFolder","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/VirtualMachineSpecification","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/VirtualMachineBundle"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"macOS virtual machines don’t have a cloud-init equivalent. Spooktacular","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provides provisioning modes to bridge this gap. Today, SSH provisioning","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is fully working. Disk-inject is in progress, and two more modes (guest"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"agent and shared-folder watcher) are planned.","type":"text"}]},{"level":3,"text":"Choosing a Mode","anchor":"Choosing-a-Mode","type":"heading"},{"header":"row","type":"table","rows":[[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Mode","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Status","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Works without setup?","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Network needed?","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Best for","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/ssh","type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Working"}]}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Need SSH enabled","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Yes","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Cloned VMs with SSH","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/diskInject","type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In progress"}]}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Yes","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"No","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Fresh IPSW installs, CI runners","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/agent","type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Planned","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Need agent installed","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"No","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"OCI images (future)","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/sharedFolder"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Planned"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Need watcher"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"No"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"No-disk-modify environments"}]}]]]},{"level":3,"text":"SSH (Working)","anchor":"SSH-Working","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"After boot, Spooktacular discovers the VM’s IP, connects via SSH,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and executes your script. You get real-time output streaming.","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"bash","type":"codeListing","code":["spook start my-vm \\","    --user-data ~\/setup.sh \\","    --provision ssh \\","    --ssh-user admin"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Requires:"}]},{"text":" Remote Login enabled in the guest","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"(System Settings -> General -> Sharing -> Remote Login).","type":"text"}]},{"level":3,"text":"Disk Inject (In Progress)","anchor":"Disk-Inject-In-Progress","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Before the VM boots, Spooktacular mounts the guest’s data volume","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and writes a standard macOS LaunchDaemon that executes your script.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This is the only mode that will work on a completely vanilla macOS","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"install. This mode is currently being implemented."}]},{"syntax":"bash","type":"codeListing","code":["spook create my-vm --from-ipsw latest \\","    --user-data ~\/setup.sh \\","    --provision disk-inject"]},{"anchor":"Guest-Agent-Planned","text":"Guest Agent (Planned)","type":"heading","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The Spooktacular guest agent will communicate over VirtIO socket — a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"direct host-guest channel that works without networking. This mode","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"is planned for a future release.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Shared-Folder-Planned","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Shared Folder (Planned)"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The script will be delivered via a VirtIO shared folder. A watcher","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"daemon in the guest will execute new scripts automatically. This","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"mode is planned for a future release.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Run scripts automatically when a VM boots."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit"],["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/CLIReference"],["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/EC2MacDeployment"],["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/GettingStarted"],["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/GitHubActionsGuide"],["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/KubernetesGuide"],["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/MLWorkloads"],["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/RemoteDesktop"],["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/BlueBubblesGuide","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/GettingStarted"],["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/BlueBubblesGuide","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/RemoteDesktop"],["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/Spo